extra_section:
I'd like to personally welcome you and Aimee to our Grade 4 Honors class at Think Academy! My name is Teacher Omar, and I have a few important notes for you as a new family.

1) Intake Phone Call or Form

I have some intake questions I’d like to ask to get to know Aimee better and develop a customized learning plan to help reach your goals. I would also love to answer any questions you may have for me. Please schedule a 15-minute parent-teacher phone call with me here: https://calendly.com/os-tutoring/think-academy-parent-chat. Note that these calls will be in English only, as I am still learning Mandarin!

If you would prefer, you can answer these intake questions via a form linked here: https://forms.gle/citeKWa84UNa2WXb7. The form is written in English and Mandarin Chinese, and can take answers in both languages. Note that you do not need to complete the form AND schedule a phone call unless you’d prefer to do so. The questions on the form are the same ones I will ask during the call.

2) My Contact Info

You can reach me via 3 modes of contact:

    Email: omar.shohoud@thethinkacademy.com
    Think Parent app: Message me directly
    Phone Call/SMS/WeChat/Whatsapp: +14254457108

You may receive text messages from a different number which I use to send out mass texts, but you should use one of the methods above to contact me. Looking forward to talking soon! Feedback is below.
notes: Since this is Aimee's first class with us, be extra warm and friendly. I also could not tell if she was engaged or not since her camera was off and she did not respond to requests to turn it on.
